channel.description:
[center][/center][size=10pt][/size]Sky Breaker 317
Client - *
Source - If you cannot connect with just the client, please fill out this form - * If I find your form passable, I may release the source.
My first server ever. It might be kinda nooby, well, at least I tried, unlike other people. Sky Breaker is a young RuneScape private server. I have been working on it for 2 months, taking constant breaks, working for hours, and having a great time while doing it. I've had experience with another server called Frontier's Fall, so I expect this one to be just a tiny bit above normal for a first server. If you have very sensitive eyes please don't look at the pictures below. They're pretty sharp. K, Sky Breaker 317 has some features and disadvantages for example...

[center][/center]Disadvantages [center][/center]Lunar Doesn't Work (Working On It) :( [center][/center]Kinda Messed Up (Fixing Most Of Server) :(
